## Learning Outcomes

After working through this repository, you will be able to:

* Understand and apply **core pandas operations** on Series and DataFrames.[1]
* Load, inspect, clean, and transform CSV datasets.[2][1]
* Use boolean filtering and conditional logic to answer questions from tabular data.[1]
* Compute descriptive statistics to interpret study and performance patterns among students.[2][1]

